data.description: 100% USDA FINANCING AVAILABLE AS WELL AS POSSIBLE DOWN PAYMENT ASSISTANCE WHICH MIGHT GET YOU IN THIS HOME WITH LITTLE TO ZERO OUT OF POCKET!!  This block home in Panama City w/EFFECTIVE YEAR 1992 (per Bay County) due to upgrades. Home is now vacant, clean, in the process of being painted, minor issues repaired, and now ready for your personal touch and updating! Good-size yard with a detached garage as well as additional carport. Attached garage has been converted to your 4th bedroom/office/den/bonus room. Late 2019 features include: newer roof, newer HVAC, new duct work, new ceiling, new carpet, new exterior doors including French doors with blinds, new garage, new carport, newer appliances. FEMA flood zone X - NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED. Minutes from the heart of Panama City, Lynn Haven, Panama City Beach and all the fun the emerald coast has to offer. Call for your showing today! ** SELLER IS LIKELY TO DO ANY REPAIRS REQUIRED FOR PASSING 4 PT.  & WIND MIT. INSPECTIONS!
